PUT {{baseUrl}}/students/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"name":"张三-更新","className":"软件工程2班","status":"enabled","remark":"已确认"}

### 删除人员（admin, 需替换真实数据库主键 id）
